bisq.core.trade

Class Trade

  • java.lang.Object
    • bisq.core.trade.Trade
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    bisq.common.Payload, bisq.common.Proto, bisq.common.proto.persistable.PersistablePayload, bisq.common.taskrunner.Model, Tradable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BuyerTrade, SellerTrade

    public abstract class Trade
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tradable, bisq.common.taskrunner.Model
    Holds all data which are relevant to the trade, but not those which are only needed in the trade process as shared data between tasks. Those data are stored in the task model.
